{"id":13979,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":5,"day":30}],"page":"12","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"世纪风","column":"","genre":"","count":"139","ytitle":"","mtitle":"火呀，你烧…","ftitle":"","authors":["庄约"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄约"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火呀，你烧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁这莽莽的平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有森林了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连鸦雀也失去了巢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火呀，你烧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁那美丽的田园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人在咀咒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劫后的断壁，颓垣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火呀，你烧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁了人间的绮梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧日的酸甜——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只留着枕边的一滴泪痕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火呀，你烧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁无数的生灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，那仇恨——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铭刻着每个人的心。"}]}